[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":346},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F":321,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F":330},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F17\u002Fmac-port-already-in-use-fix\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":302,"date":303,"description":18,"extension":304,"lang":305,"meta":306,"navigation":307,"path":308,"readingMinutes":309,"seo":310,"standalone":311,"stem":312,"tags":313,"tldr":317,"updated":318,"url":319,"__hash__":320},"content\u002F雜談\u002FMac-系統-Port-號被佔用的解決方式-Mac-Port-xxx-is-already-in-use.md","Mac 系統 Port 號被佔用的解決方式(Mac Port xxx is already in use)","241830554",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":291},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,31,37,53,56,65,72,75,106,115,125,134,140,143,154,158,165,168,172,179,188,191,197,204,209,216,220,226,232,235,239,242,248,251,257,263,267,270,273,279,282,287],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"開發系統時可能會出現一種狀況，也就是 Port 被佔用，因此會出現類似這種訊息「Port 5000 is already in use」，所以就寫一篇來紀錄一下如何解決 Port 被佔用的問題。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"查看-port","查看 Port",[16,24,25,26,30],{},"首先當你發現伺服器跟你說「Port ",[27,28,29],"code",{},"xxxx"," is already in use」的時候，你可以打開終端機，試著輸入以下指令查看 Port 是不是真的被佔用",[16,32,33,34,36],{},"(",[27,35,29],{}," 替換成你被佔用的 Port)",[38,39,44],"pre",{"className":40,"code":41,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","lsof -i:xxxx\n","cmd","",[27,45,46],{"__ignoreMap":43},[47,48,51],"span",{"class":49,"line":50},"line",1,[47,52,41],{},[16,54,55],{},"例如我查詢 5000 Port 的狀況",[38,57,59],{"className":40,"code":58,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"lsof -i:5000\n",[27,60,61],{"__ignoreMap":43},[47,62,63],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,64,58],{},[16,66,67],{},[68,69],"img",{"alt":70,"src":71},"lsof","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-17%2014.03.09.png",[16,73,74],{},"畫面上可以看到有以下欄位",[76,77,78,82,85,88,91,94,97,100,103],"ul",{},[79,80,81],"li",{},"COMMAND",[79,83,84],{},"PID",[79,86,87],{},"USER",[79,89,90],{},"FD",[79,92,93],{},"TYPE",[79,95,96],{},"DEVICE",[79,98,99],{},"SIZE\u002FOFF",[79,101,102],{},"NODE",[79,104,105],{},"NAME",[16,107,108,109,111,112,114],{},"你只需要特別注意兩個東西，也就是 ",[27,110,81],{}," 跟 ",[27,113,84],{},"。",[16,116,117,118,121,122],{},"如果你無法輸入 ",[27,119,120],{},"lsof -i:xxxx"," 的話，你可以試著加上 ",[27,123,124],{},"sudo",[38,126,128],{"className":40,"code":127,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"sudo lsof -i:5000\n",[27,129,130],{"__ignoreMap":43},[47,131,132],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,133,127],{},[16,135,136,137,139],{},"透過上圖中的 ",[27,138,81],{}," 我們可以知道是 Node 在佔用 Port，因此你可以試著翻一下是不是哪一個視窗忘記中止了。",[16,141,142],{},"如果你想要看全部有被使用的 Port 的話，則輸入以下",[38,144,148],{"className":145,"code":146,"language":147,"meta":43,"style":43},"language-node shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","lsof -n -i\n","node",[27,149,150],{"__ignoreMap":43},[47,151,152],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,153,146],{},[12,155,157],{"id":156},"停止釋放清除-port","停止\u002F釋放\u002F清除 Port",[16,159,160,161,164],{},"如果你真的找不到這個啟動來源時，你可以試著輸入 ",[27,162,163],{},"kill PID"," 來清除被佔用的 Port。",[16,166,167],{},"以剛剛的範例圖來講",[16,169,170],{},[68,171],{"alt":70,"src":71},[16,173,174,175,178],{},"我們可以看到 PID 是 ",[27,176,177],{},"19625","，因此就輸入以下指令即可",[38,180,182],{"className":40,"code":181,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"kill 19625\n",[27,183,184],{"__ignoreMap":43},[47,185,186],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,187,181],{},[16,189,190],{},"輸入完畢後你並不會得到任何回饋",[16,192,193],{},[68,194],{"alt":195,"src":196},"kill","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-17%2014.14.48.png",[16,198,199,200,203],{},"但是你再去輸入一次 ",[27,201,202],{},"lsof -i:5000"," 就會發現沒有任何東西回應給你哩。",[16,205,206],{},[68,207],{"alt":70,"src":208},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-17%2014.15.02.png",[16,210,211,212,215],{},"如果你有開著 Server 終端機的話，或許會發現 Server 終端機噴出這個訊息「",[27,213,214],{},"[1] 19624 terminated  npm start","」囉~",[12,217,219],{"id":218},"無法被釋放的-5000-port","無法被釋放的 5000 Port",[16,221,222,223,225],{},"Mac 有一個特有的問題，就是 5000 Port 會被莫名其妙佔用，而且這個佔用也很機車，你不管怎麼 ",[27,224,195],{}," 都會長出來",[16,227,228],{},[68,229],{"alt":230,"src":231},"無法釋放的 5000 Port","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-17%2014.30.50.png",[16,233,234],{},"這個問題主要是出在 Mac 控制中心有一個東西佔用了 5000 Port",[236,237,238],"h3",{"id":238},"解決方式",[16,240,241],{},"首先先開啟「系統偏好設定」，然後在上方搜尋「共享」",[16,243,244],{},[68,245],{"alt":246,"src":247},"共享","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-17%2014.35.18.png",[16,249,250],{},"接下來進入到共享後，找到「Airplay 接收器」欄位，然後取消打勾即可",[16,252,253],{},[68,254],{"alt":255,"src":256},"Airplay","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2022-01-17_14_40_22.png",[16,258,259,260,262],{},"接下來再去查 ",[27,261,202],{}," 就不會發生佔用了～",[236,264,266],{"id":265},"_2023-更新解決方式","2023 更新解決方式",[16,268,269],{},"由於後來 Mac 系統有更新一版，把整個 UI 介面更新，所以我們要找的地方也有所變動。",[16,271,272],{},"首先先開啟「系統偏好設定」，然後在上方搜尋「AirPlay 接收器」",[16,274,275],{},[68,276],{"alt":277,"src":278},"AirPlay","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-03-07%2010.13.55.png",[16,280,281],{},"接下來進入到 AirPlay 接收器後，找到「AirPlay 接收器」欄位，然後取消打勾即可",[16,283,284],{},[68,285],{"alt":277,"src":286},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-03-07%2010.15.47.png",[288,289,290],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":43,"searchDepth":292,"depth":292,"links":293},2,[294,295,296,297],{"id":14,"depth":292,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":292,"text":22},{"id":156,"depth":292,"text":157},{"id":218,"depth":292,"text":219,"children":298},[299,301],{"id":238,"depth":300,"text":238},3,{"id":265,"depth":300,"text":266},"雜談","2022-01-17 13:57:30","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fmac-port-mac-port-xxx-is-already-in-use","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"雜談\u002FMac-系統-Port-號被佔用的解決方式-Mac-Port-xxx-is-already-in-use",[314,315,316],"Port 佔用","Mac","障礙排除",null,"2023-03-07 10:15:00","\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F","uGnnJVw19sBk3KQm3NFZM8C0Ffc9fuN3eXkz4Z12QAU",{"newer":322,"older":326},{"url":323,"title":324,"date":325},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20220118\u002F1578337381\u002F","關於 JavaScript 常見的 Multiple left-hand assignment 考題","2022-01-18 09:09:39",{"url":327,"title":328,"date":329},"\u002Fnuxt\u002F20220116\u002F3415794445\u002F","Nuxt.js 2.x 實戰手冊(7) - Axios","2022-01-16 18:12:30",[331,336,341],{"url":332,"title":333,"date":334,"readingMinutes":335},"\u002Fother\u002F20260710\u002F2193411838\u002F","關於我做了百日挑戰「增肌減脂」這個有趣的實驗","2026-07-10 09:53:56","16",{"url":337,"title":338,"date":339,"readingMinutes":340},"\u002Fother\u002F20260623\u002F2826413095\u002F","Mac 系統監控工具就推薦用 Stats！一款免費又開源，還能看 CPU、GPU、溫度、網速的軟體","2026-06-23 10:00:00","4",{"url":342,"title":343,"date":344,"readingMinutes":345},"\u002Fother\u002F20260526\u002F2846301957\u002F","寫部落格能月入幾萬美金嗎？聊聊 Google AdSense 真實收益與計算方式","2026-05-26 21:00:00","5",1784011726819]